<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天是寒假前的最后一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们互相交换礼物，和对方说再见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比走向儿童中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真不敢相信今天是学校的最后一天。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天不是学校的最后一天。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“学校的最后一天在六月。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是今年学校的最后一天！” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师吹了吹哨子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要过新年了，大家兴奋吗？” 她问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而且要放假了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了。但是我们今天要做什么？” 贾森说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天是今年儿童中心活动的最后一天！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要玩儿一个游戏，叫环绕世界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师拿起塑料垫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个垫上有一个英文字母。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！我喜欢环绕世界！” 波比欢呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些字母是儿童中心Kids Central的英文拼写。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把塑料垫放在地上，摆成了半圆形。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先从字母K开始投篮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104277</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果球进了，就移到字母I。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谁最靠近字母L，谁就赢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我先来！” 莉琪边说边跑到字母K的位置。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师给她球，大家排好了队。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪投了第一个球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“成功了！” 她欢呼道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都投了两次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他们站在字母D的位置。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪又成功了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比不敢相信莉琪这么厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今年，她的篮球进步很大！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜没投进。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦和贾森投进了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在轮到波比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>投篮很容易，但是波比很紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是他今年的最后一场比赛！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把球投出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>球碰到篮板，进了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“移到字母S！” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>字母E就在篮球架前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪、伊坦、贾森和波比都投进了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在字母N，贾森没有投进。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抱怨说：“我差点就环绕世界了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着他笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，对我来说已经很不错了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪、伊坦和波比继续投篮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都在字母T和R投进了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了字母A，伊坦没有投进。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？” 他大喊，“怎么回事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和尼娜和贾森一起坐在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜说：“莉琪加油！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以的，波比！” 贾森鼓着掌说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪对波比笑了笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来了！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她投出球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！” 进球时她大声欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比拍着球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不能输给一个三年级的女生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他投出球……球进了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今年的环绕世界冠军是莉琪和波比！” 雪莉老师宣布说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们两个都很棒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。” 莉琪笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“比赛很精彩。” 伊坦对他们俩说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪对波比说：“你要小心哦！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，你就会有一个篮球对手了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一整个假期，他都要练习篮球了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他要在明年打败莉琪！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>